<p align="center"><img src="/images/stories/logos.jpg" /></p>
<p>Santie O’Connell and her husband have been changing their lifestyles over the years, becoming more and more energy efficient. They live in Kimberley in the Northern Cape, which has very extreme temperatures of hot summers and cold winters.&nbsp;</td>
